5. Fees
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
&BANKNAVN. may charge a fee for the services provided to
you. &BANKNAVN. may also charge a fee for responding to enquiries from
public authorities.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
These fees are charged either as a fixed amount for the service
provided or as a percentage or hourly rate relative to the scope
of the service. The calculation methods can be combined.
.sp 3mm
&BANKNAVN.'s standard fees can be seen on a price list which is
available at the bank. Information about other fees is available upon
request.
