6. Overdraft interest and reminder fees etc.
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
If your account becomes overdrawn or is used in conflict with the
agreement, &BANKNAVN. may charge overdraft interest/commission or
default interest and a fee for sending out reminder letters as well as
expenses for legal assistance in connection with debt collection etc.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
The size of the reminder fee is specified in &BANKNAVN.'s reminder letter.
Information about overdraft interest etc. is available upon request.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
The overdraft interest/overdraft commission is fixed on the basis of
&BANKNAVN.'s assessment of the risk of defaulted claims in general and
the individual defaulted claim specifically.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
&BANKNAVN. may at any time choose, administratively and
financially, to cease the adding of interest on defaulted claims. Such
omission to add interest which has not been agreed with you
is not to be regarded as a waiver by &BANKNAVN. of the right to
charge interest on its claim and demand payment of any costs later
incurred. This applies irrespective of whether you are informed of
the bookkeeping method used via an account statement or otherwise.
