:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
.us Changing agreement terms
.br
If special terms have been agreed with you, they are stated in the 'Special
conditions' section of the document.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
When determining the terms of the relationship between you and
&BANKNAVN., &BANKNAVN. takes into consideration the total volume of your
business.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
Therefore, if any changes are made to the volume of business which have
not been agreed with &BANKNAVN., &BANKNAVN. reserves the right to change
the agreement terms at the same time.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.us Termination
.br
You and &BANKNAVN. are entitled to terminate the customer relationship
without notice at any time.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
When the customer relationship ceases, &BANKNAVN. is entitled to
terminate any guarantee commitments, including liabilities in foreign
currencies, and to be released from other commitments assumed on your
behalf. You are obliged to release &BANKNAVN. from all commitments
undertaken on your behalf, and, if necessary, to provide security for
such commitments.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.us Offsetting
.br
&BANKNAVN. may without prior notice offset any claim due on your part
against any claim that you may have now or in future against
&BANKNAVN., unless otherwise agreed with &BANKNAVN..
