9. Various provisions
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
.us Power of attorney
.br
You may give others power of attorney to act on your behalf in
relation to &BANKNAVN.. A power of attorney must be made in
writing, normally using &BANKNAVN.'s power of attorney form. The
power of attorney is valid until &BANKNAVN. receives written
notification from you that it has been revoked or changed.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
If the principal dies, the power of attorney expires when &BANKNAVN. is
notified of the principal's death. This means that the principal's
accounts etc. are blocked until the probate court has decided how the
estate should be administered. This also applies to joint accounts.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.us Recording telephone conversations
.br
In order to provide you with the proper service, &BANKNAVN. may record
its telephone conversations with you.
Usually this is only done in connection with securities and currency
trading.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.us Conducting business abroad
.br
If &BANKNAVN. is to conduct business abroad on your
behalf, &BANKNAVN. will choose a business partner for
this, unless otherwise agreed. &BANKNAVN. is not liable for any
errors committed by the bank used or for its creditworthiness.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
If you hold foreign securities in custody with &BANKNAVN., &BANKNAVN. is
liable for any potential errors committed by
the foreign bank and for its creditworthiness, unless you
have chosen the business partner yourself.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
The rules of law, customs and business terms of a foreign country may
differ considerably from those applying in Denmark. To the extent that
&BANKNAVN. is subject to foreign rules of law, customs or business
terms, these also apply to you.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
