.us Guarantee Fund for Depositors and Investors
.br
As a customer of &BANKNAVN., the Guarantee Fund for Depositors and
Investors offers you some degree of protection against losses in the event
that the bank should be declared bankrupt or suspend its payments.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
