up to an amount of EUR 100,000 per depositor.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
The Guarantee Fund also covers any losses suffered by you as an
investor as a result of &BANKNAVN.'s inability to return the securities
which are held or managed by &BANKNAVN..
The Guarantee Fund provides compensation of up to EUR 20,000 per
investor. The Guarantee Fund for Depositors and Investors has published
a leaflet where you can read more about how you are covered. You can
request a copy of the leaflet at
.us www.garantifonden.dk
