.us Breach and other events of default
.br
In the following special situations, &BANKNAVN. is entitled to terminate
the loan/credit without notice and demand immediate payment of the entire
outstanding balance:
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.of 3mm
a)¤If payments, interest, commission or instalments are not paid when
due, and you have not paid eight days after &BANKNAVN. has sent you
a reminder to the address last known by &BANKNAVN.. The above also
applies to credits if you exceed the credit maximum without
approval from &BANKNAVN..
.of
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.of 3mm
b)¤If you become subject to individual legal proceedings in the form of
execution or attachment.
.of
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.of 3mm
c)¤If you become subject to reorganisation, file for bankruptcy, begin
debt restructuring proceedings or the Danish Business Authority decides
to request that the probate court dissolve the company.
.of
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.of 3mm
d)¤If you die.
.of
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.of 3mm
e)¤If you take up permanent residence outside Denmark and no prior
agreement on the (future) payment of the loan/credit has been made.
.of
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.of 3mm
f)¤If you have supplied incorrect information affecting the granting of
the loan/credit.
.of
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.of 3mm
g)¤If you do not file a tax return, tax assessment notice or annual report
(if applicable) at &BANKNAVN.'s request.
.of
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.of 3mm
h)¤If you do not have the annual report audited at &BANKNAVN.'s request
even if you are not required to do so by law.
.of
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.of 3mm
i)¤If you do not accept &BANKNAVN.'s request for renegotiation of the
credit within the deadline specified.
.of
.sp 3mm
.kp on
If the loan/credit is secured by a guarantee, and the
guarantor(s) becomes subject to one or more of the events
described in item b).
Or if the guarantor(s) have supplied incorrect information
affecting the granting of the loan, &BANKNAVN. may terminate the
loan/credit at three months' notice if no other security
acceptable to &BANKNAVN. is furnished within one month.
