.us Use of payments
.br
Payments from guarantors will first be used to cover
interest, commission and costs and then to reduce the secured debt.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
Where the loan/credit is only partly secured under guarantee, your
payments will first be used for repayment of the unsecured part.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.us Enforcement of security and recourse
.br
&BANKNAVN. reserves the right to enforce any security provided by you or
by third parties and to write off the proceeds at &BANKNAVN.'s
discretion. The guarantor thus has no right of recourse in relation to
such security.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
This means, for example
.sp 3mm
.of 3mm
-¤that &BANKNAVN. may, without the guarantor's approval, release other
security for the guaranteed commitment
.br
.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 3mm
