Special terms and conditions concerning security
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
.us 1. Deterioration of security
.br
If the value of the security diminishes significantly, &BANKNAVN. may
demand that you either make an extraordinary repayment on the
debt/credit limit, or that you post additional security to offset the
deterioration in value. If you fail to do so, &BANKNAVN. may consider
this material breach of the loan/credit conditions.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
If &BANKNAVN. holds security in property, &BANKNAVN. will not demand
extraordinary repayment or additional security in the event of the value
diminishing, unless the fall in value is attributable to neglect.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.us 2. &BANKNAVN.'s rights regarding the pledged assets
.br
&BANKNAVN. may utilise all the rights of the pledger to the pledged
assets, including receiving and signing for any and all sums stemming
from the pledged assets, terminating and collecting, signing for and
conveying pledged claims and mortgage deeds to itself or a third party.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
On exercising these rights, the present document shall constitute
authorisation for &BANKNAVN. - in relation to the public registration
authorities as well.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
On the mortgaging of shares, unit trusts and the
like, &BANKNAVN. may, solely on the basis of the
present document, exercise all the rights that
holders of shares and unit trusts may enjoy pursuant
to the applicable corporate legislation, company
articles of association, any shareholder agreements
and the like.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
If the security comprises an insurance policy, the pledger is obliged, on
request, to present &BANKNAVN. with receipts proving the timely payment of
the associated premiums.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
If &BANKNAVN. chooses to seek satisfaction of its claim in the buy-back
value of the policy, &BANKNAVN. will be entitled to do so without
applying the period of notice stated in the Danish Insurance Contracts
Act (Forsikringsaftaleloven).
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
&BANKNAVN. is under no obligation to seek coverage in advance in the
security posted, and &BANKNAVN. is free to choose its approach with
regard to utilisation in relation to your commitment as a whole.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.us 3. Expenses related to the security
.br
&BANKNAVN. may demand payment of fees for pledged assets.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
&BANKNAVN. may also demand payment to cover the bank's
expenses for safeguarding its interests as pledgee, including
any expenses for the payment of insurance premiums, inspection
of the pledged assets, expenses for legal aid and so on.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.us 4. Return on the pledged assets
.br
The pledge arrangement includes interest and dividends of any and
all kinds on the pledged assets, including bonuses on life
insurance policies, any free shares and subscription rights linked
to shares, rental income and the like.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
&BANKNAVN. is entitled but not obliged (not even in relation to
guarantors) to receive any interest and dividends for the payment of
instalments, interest and costs.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.us 5. Messages
.br
The pledger is obliged to pass on to &BANKNAVN. without delay any and all
messages the pledger receives regarding the pledged assets.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.us 6. Drawing of bonds
.br
If pledged bonds are drawn and new bonds are purchased to replace those
drawn, &BANKNAVN. is entitled to request that VP SECURITIES register
same as having been mortgaged to &BANKNAVN..
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.us 7. Enforcement
.br
Any enforcement of mortgage rights will be carried out after notice in
advance to the pledger through compulsory sale or in any other way
considered appropriate by &BANKNAVN., including enforcement through
&BANKNAVN.'s own measures.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
