.kp on
.us Scope of the security
.br
Security and guarantees serve as surety for the payment of
capital, interest, commission, case costs and other expenses paid
in connection with the collection of the debt in accordance with
the present agreement.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
The assets pledged also serve as security for any other obligation you
may owe to &BANKNAVN. and/or any of its branches - either currently or
in the future.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
