.us Avoidance
.br
If, in connection with your bankruptcy or similar, additional security
used for whole or partial settlement of the claim secured under the
guarantee is deemed void pursuant to Chapter 8 of the Danish Bankruptcy
Act (Konkursloven), the guarantee obligation will remain in force. The
same applies in the event of payment made by you being deemed a
voidable transaction.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
