.us 5. Completing final settlement through netting
.br
When final settlement is carried out through netting, the present value of
the receivables of &BANKNAVN. and the borrower is calculated in Danish
kroner or another currency agreed upon. &BANKNAVN.'s and your receivables
are settled so as to constitute one net balance.
.br
Receivables which are secured through a financial security agreement
and other security are written down by the proceeds from security
enforced. The calculated receivables are then included in the final
settlement.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
