facilities, such as loans and credits, is the total remaining debt
as at the calculation date, including added unpaid interest plus
interest and costs accrued but not added. The calculation comprises
compensation for capital losses resulting from early repayment and a
preliminary determination of claims according to commitments which
can only be determined at a later date, for example guarantee commitments.
.br
.kp off
.kp on
