When becoming a customer of &BANKNAVN., you must state your name, address
and civil registration (CPR) number or business registration
number (civil reg. no./CVR no.).
You must present photo ID, such as a passport or driving licence, and
other ID with your civil reg. no./CVR no. and current address printed
on it.
