2. Collecting and processing information about you
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
.us Collecting and using personal information
.br
When a new customer joins &BANKNAVN., we collect information such as
name, address and civil reg. no./CVR no. for use in our offering of
financial services of any kind, including customer advice, customer
care, customer management, credit check and marketing.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
When a customer uses payment services, including credit and debit
cards, cheques, online banking etc., we collect information from
shops, banks and other sources. Information is also collected when a
customer uses a cheque. The information is collected only to enable
&BANKNAVN. to execute the payment transaction correctly and prepare
account statements, payment summaries etc.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
Moreover, &BANKNAVN. collects information from the Danish Central Office
of Civil Registration (among other things with a view to updating
address information) and from other publicly accessible sources and
registers. When performing a credit check of you, &BANKNAVN. collects
information from credit information agencies and blacklists. Please also
note that &BANKNAVN. continuously updates information about
you by collecting information from the Danish Office of Civil
Registration as well as credit information agencies and blacklists
approved by the Danish Data Protection Agency (including
'Kreditvagten' and 'Aktiv Kreditsikring'). You can always contact
&BANKNAVN. for information about the sources from which we collect
such information.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
You are not obliged to provide &BANKNAVN. with the requested
information, but &BANKNAVN. may need the information in order to give
you sound and professional advice and to consider requests for a loan or
other services.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.us Duty of confidentiality
.br
&BANKNAVN.'s employees are required to keep all your affairs
confidential and may not without permission disclose or pass on any
information which comes to their attention in the course of their work
at &BANKNAVN.. The rules on confidentiality are laid down in the
Danish Financial Services Act (Lov om finansiel virksomhed).
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.us Disclosing information
.br
In order to fulfil any agreements made with you, for example for the
transfer of money to another person, we will disclose the information
which is necessary to identify you and fulfil the agreement.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
