you to credit information agencies and/or blacklists in accordance with
the applicable rules.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
&BANKNAVN. may disclose information to other loan providers or leasing
companies without your consent if the information is to be used for
risk management purposes, including credit check and administration.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
Usual customer information, such as your name, address and civil
reg. no./CVR no., may be disclosed to other companies for the
purpose of handling administrative tasks. Moreover, usual customer
information about you may be disclosed to other financial companies
for advisory and marketing purposes. The recipient of information is
or will also be subject to a duty of confidentiality. A list of
companies with which &BANKNAVN. exchanges information can be
obtained from one of our branches.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
